<div id="outline-container-orgf766686" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgf766686">Org-roam</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgf766686">
<p>
Org-roam is a plain-text knowledge management system. It brings some of <a href="https://roamresearch.com/">Roam's</a> more powerful features into the Org-mode ecosystem.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-emacs-lisp">(<span style="color: #ff79c6; font-weight: bold;">use-package</span> <span style="color: #8be9fd;">org-roam</span> 
  <span style="color: #ffb86c;">:ensure</span> t
  <span style="color: #ffb86c;">:custom</span>
  (org-roam-directory (file-truename <span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"~/org/org-roam"</span>))
  <span style="color: #ffb86c;">:bind</span> ((<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"C-c n l"</span> . org-roam-buffer-toggle)
         (<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"C-c n f"</span> . org-roam-node-find)
         (<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"C-c n i"</span> . org-roam-node-insert)
         (<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"C-c n d"</span> . org-roam-dailies-capture-today)
         (<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"C-c n y"</span> . org-roam-dailies-capture-yesterday)
         (<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"C-c n t"</span> . org-roam-dailies-capture-tomorrow)
         <span style="color: #6272a4;">;; </span><span style="color: #6272a4;">Org-roam UI binds</span>
         (<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"C-c n u"</span> . org-roam-ui-mode)
         (<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"C-c n g"</span> . org-roam-ui-open))
  <span style="color: #ffb86c;">:config</span>
  (org-roam-setup))
</pre>
</div>
</div>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li><a id="org53629c5"></a>llama<br />
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-org53629c5">
<p>
llama is a dependency of org-roam, and must have the repository manually specified.
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-emacs-lisp">(<span style="color: #ff79c6; font-weight: bold;">use-package</span> <span style="color: #8be9fd;">llama</span>
  <span style="color: #ffb86c;">:ensure</span>
  (<span style="color: #ffb86c;">:host</span> github <span style="color: #ffb86c;">:repo</span> <span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"yasuhirokimura/llama"</span> <span style="color: #ffb86c;">:branch</span> <span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"main"</span> <span style="color: #ffb86c;">:files</span> (<span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"*.el"</span> <span style="color: #f1fa8c;">"out"</span>)))
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</li>
